Key_60.Set1: Hard To Handle, Doin' That Rag, Good Morning Little School Girl, Morning Dew, Sitting On Top Of The World, Turn On Your Love Light
Key_60.Comment:
Jerry Plays Glide Guitar On Hard To Handle.
According To Ron Ramsey, Who Attended The Show, The Other Bands On The Bill Were Src (A Local Group), And The Velvet Underground. The Velvet Underground Played A Very Long Set And As A Result The Dead Only Got To Play One Set On This Date.
According To Ramsey The Dead Did The Same Thing To The Velvet Underground The Next Night.
